<br>
Living Huts are located throughout the tribe for old and new Athelfi who choose to stay in Smyrna for a night or long term. Stables,a blacksmith, an eatery hut, and a sweat hut can also be located in the growing tribe.<br>
<br>
The Amazon Tribe of Smyrna is gaurded twenty-four hours a day,and those wishing to enter the tribe must do so through the tribal gates.<br>
